00:34:37,293 --> 00:34:42,298
Rashad talked about the sunflowers and the
ants that crawl under them. And the alligators in Florida.

404
00:34:43,450 --> 00:34:48,055
All of them with hearts beating. All of them needing food, nutrients. The system is incredible.

405
00:34:48,055 --> 00:34:51,107
It is such a complex interlocking system,

406
00:34:51,107 --> 00:34:56,764
right down to the tiniest cell and its components,
which we are down to quarks at this point.

407
00:34:56,764 --> 00:34:59,215
Everything has its provisions.

