410
00:35:09,227 --> 00:35:13,130
And I watched him. He was walking, walking down the road,

411
00:35:13,130 --> 00:35:16,783
not flying in a jet convoy, but still walking
with a tripod,

412
00:35:16,783 --> 00:35:20,787
the same kind of, I don't know, George Washington
used or Galileo used,

413
00:35:20,787 --> 00:35:24,190
peering through a tube to establish a straight eye

414
00:35:24,190 --> 00:35:27,092
And I thought, we've come so far and we've
done nothing.

415
00:35:27,292 --> 00:35:29,392
We've just done nothing. We're still walking.

416
00:35:29,642 --> 00:35:31,141
We're, we're still walking.

417
00:35:31,442 --> 00:35:38,651
Surely, there's another way from a satellite or something to do what he had to do by walking and setting up this awkward instrument.

418
00:35:39,603 --> 00:35:41,353
Provisions for all things.

419
00:35:43,553 --> 00:35:45,803
