00:35:57,614 --> 00:36:05,024
those that come to him that appear not to
be perhaps as wealthy or as well-situated as others.

424
00:36:05,675 --> 00:36:12,183
I think he was chastised for ignoring a person
like that and tending to someone else over him.

425
00:36:12,834 --> 00:36:15,836
We don't know other people's choices.

426
00:36:16,396 --> 00:36:22,832
We have no idea what their eventual choice,
their eventual place is going to be in the Eternal Life.

427
00:36:22,832 --> 00:36:24,832
And it's not for us to judge.

428
00:36:24,832 --> 00:36:30,939
It is for us to forsake the material world
and hence our own egos, our own bodies

429
00:36:30,939 --> 00:36:39,100
that we pay so much attention to and take care of the world around us. For all we know these are our family, our real family.

430
00:36:39,300 --> 00:36:42,252
And we wouldn't know that. We have no way of knowing that.

431
00:36:44,252 --> 00:36:47,655
[93:11]  You shall proclaim the blessing your Lord has bestowed upon you.

432
00:36:47,655 --> 00:36:49,655
Mã Shã Allãh. Alhamdu Lillah.

433
00:36:50,657 --> 00:36:51,906
IN SHAA ALLAH.

