at the same time.

445
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:43,603
Words come out of our mouths very quickly. We don't think about them.

446
00:37:44,254 --> 00:37:46,254
Sometimes we just speak.

447
00:37:46,805 --> 00:37:52,963
And we need to be careful. I've taught myself any number of times after that (unintelligible)

448
00:37:52,963 --> 00:37:59,542
