449
00:37:59,542 --> 00:38:02,089
He allows the things to happen that
need to happen for us.

450
00:38:02,089 --> 00:38:08,474
So, it's very easy to make a mistake, cross over the line and say "I'm sick because God wanted me to be sick for this reason."

451
00:38:09,101 --> 00:38:10,101
That's not it.

452
00:38:11,854 --> 00:38:17,412
So, we need to be very careful and only talk
about the good things that God does.

